{
  "texts": [
    "We only considered English tweets; thus, when requesting the Twitter API, we always attached the LANG:EN command to the query.",
    "We defined a general time window of interest starting from January 01, 2007, until October, 31, 2022.",
    "This means that we considered Twitter activity in a time window of almost 15 years, representing a comprehensive time period including various global and local historical events.",
    "Tweet preprocessingWe preprocessed the collected tweets by removing unfavorable characters to obtain standardized, usable tweets.",
    "We removed URLs, several irregular characters (regular expression of allowed characters: [A-ZA-Z0-9) and transformed the tweet to lowercase."
  ]
}